{"tid":1632511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有邊間鋪係呢兩日仲營業","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:44:29.000Z","uid":121068,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7bda5d68cacde32d282afc4f01594c9b3fe412","tid":1632511,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:18:14.000Z","msg":"意思係示威區入面既商鋪<br />\n例如cwb <br />\n全部鋪都收曬檔 點解你地仲要員工番工<br />\n佢地既命唔係命 賺錢最緊要？<br />\n你地口講自己良心企業 <br />\n實質做緊既野賤過狗 <br />\n<br />\n有邊間鋪係早兩日仲係示威區<br />\n要員工番工甚或要佢地收好夜<br />\n你地都要顧下員工安全架 <br />\n我知賺錢重要 但人身安全呢<br />\n<br />\n特別要指名某幾間鋪 見到下午4-5點放曬tg<br />\n都仲有員工係鋪入面做野開門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 我唔係佢地員工"},{"pid":"030c23110e5fbd5681c2b6c4b09d5a6cf304fcea","tid":1632511,"uid":121068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:20:15.000Z","msg":"cwb收工仲要員工食住tg走 <br />\n仲要無車呀 <br />\n<br />\n有邊幾間鋪有開"},{"pid":"1a771ed4fcbabe7832b0bcb12480b48aeea64398","tid":1632511,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890fe5713607aeb071919a70e391809681b55d27","tid":1632511,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599df27464508d29367d4b6b744cec6abb34d438","tid":1632511,"uid":73089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:25:19.000Z","msg":"唔好又開支線啦<br />\n開得嘅都係小店 分分鐘自己係老闆  關你鬼事咩 你理掂啲手足先"},{"pid":"c42b6cef4a0f6c89ec45762e241d80844796dfe8","tid":1632511,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry